statements: SELECT * FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed
SELECT feed_name, protein_content, carbohydrate_content, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed
SELECT feed_id, feed_name, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed ORDER BY protein_content DESC
SELECT * FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed WHERE carbohydrate_content > 15
SELECT feed_name, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed WHERE protein_content < 10
SELECT feed_id, feed_name, protein_content, carbohydrate_content, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed ORDER BY feed_name ASC;
SELECT feed_name, protein_content, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed WHERE protein_content >= 10 AND carbohydrate_content <= 20;
SELECT * FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed WHERE fat_content > protein_content AND carbohydrate_content < fat_content ORDER BY fat_content DESC, protein_content ASC;
SELECT feed_name, fat_content FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed WHERE protein_content BETWEEN 15 AND 20;

SELECT feed_id, SUM(protein_content) AS total_protein, SUM(carbohydrate_content) AS total_carbohydrate FROM nutritional_composition_of_feed GROUP BY feed_id HAVING total_protein > 50 AND total_carbohydrate < 30;

SELECT f.farm_name, l.species, fc.protein_content, fc.fat_content FROM farm f JOIN livestock l ON f.farm_id = l.feed_id JOIN feed_composition fc ON l.feed_id = fc.feed_id WHERE fc.fiber_content < 0.1;
